...As for Vega, you see. She drinks a lot of water while

\SE[4]Huh? It's pitch black. \SE[0]Did you already go to
sleep?

\SE[2]I wonder if she's upstairs? \!\SE[3]Should I turn on
the lights?

\SE[0]Ah, welcome back. \SE[0]You're back earlier than I
thought. [2]Do you have any souvenirs?

\SE[33]As for souvenirs... \!\SE[1]I got some winter snow
melt cream puffs. \!\SE[33]They're made with specialty eggs
and the custard inside melts in your mouth, it's
irresistibly delicious.

\SE[17]Cream puffs...!? \SE[42]Winter snow melt...!!?
\SE[40]Huh, well? \SE[68]If that's the case, should I also
exempt you from the crime of leaving me behind? Is that
okay?

\SE[4]I'll leave it here. \!\SE[3]Ah, I should call Vita
too.

\SE[2]In that case, I'll go. \!\SE[1]I want to say I'm home
to Lunaroa too.

\SE[4]As for the battle... \!\SE[75]I was so enthusiastic
that I didn't have any work to do. \!\SE[51]But deep down...
I wonder...

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you see. She drinks a lot of water while
studying... so she ends up going to the bathroom... quite
frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
